column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID,p.absMagU, p.absMagG, p.absMagR, p.absMagI, p.absMagZ, p.z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoZ p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
